Resumo da Regra de Ouro do Cloud Run: Alterou qualquer arquivo (HTML, Python, CSS)? -> Tem de fazer Build e depois Deploy.

 gcloud builds submit --tag us-central1-docker.pkg.dev/ivory-cycle-279202/mongocrud-repo/api-mongocrud:v1 .
 
 gcloud run deploy api-mongocrud \
    --image us-central1-docker.pkg.dev/ivory-cycle-279202/mongocrud-repo/api-mongocrud:v1 \
    --platform managed \
    --region us-central1 \
    --allow-unauthenticated \
    --set-env-vars MONGO_URI="mongodb+srv://alfacentauri:manga2029@clusteraprender.xtrjxzz.mongodb.net/",MONGO_DB="app_db"

